(Where did this whole baby thing come from? Aren't they both guys?)
Starscream

Starscream watched Dollen go.

"Come back!" but he knew he could do nothing. What was he talking 
about before? But now things looked even worse. 5 of them had left, 
the numbers were dwindling. Maybe it wasn't such a good idea to elect 
Phobia to lead. There were only seven left, and two of them were near 
death! Starscream pleaded again with Phobia.

"I guess will go with The Alliance now. If that's all right with you."

Than Starscream whispered something in Drillbit's ear.

"Becareful. I don't know if we can trust Phobia. I don't know if I 
can trust you, but most probably yes. I don't know if KitKat's safety 
is the important thing on his agenda. Remember, if you need me, i'm 
just a comm message away. And watch Megatron carefully if you see 
him."

Starscream turned to the Alliance member.

"I guess I'll be going with you now."
______________________________________________________________________
Brix

Brix lifted up Ramulus' spark, and carefully placed it in one hand. 
Of course it was floating, but you get the idea. He removed Fliq's 
chest plate, and than got ready to place Ramulus' spark in the body.

"Let's just hope it isn't too late."

Brix placed the spark inside Fliq's body and closed the plate.
______________________________________________________________________
The Trainers

A transmission came in from Ignatius.

"Lord Prebon! I've spotted Savage two sectors down."

"Excellent Ignatius! Keep an eye on him and inform us of any moves. 
Blaze, pick up his scent and find the exact position. We'll soon have 
him!"

The 5 bots continued down their path.
